Dear Mariyaiya,

I have reviewed the v2.2 document submitted today. The content is 
excellent and this is the most complete FSD in the SPINRISE project. 
Before I record CEO approval, two text corrections must be made to the 
Document Identity table.

*What the document has achieved*

All 20 IST questions are answered and resolved. All 12 defects directed 
in the CEO review mail are in Section 12 as Rec 17 through Rec 28, each 
with a specific QuestPDF fix. The three-level approval workflow is 
documented in Section 5.5a with Palanivel's confirmation, the web 
approval URL, and both screen names. Section 10 has the full approval 
screen detail. Section 11 has the Pallavaa division-wise stock 
variation. The po_para 63-column audit with 10 unused columns identified 
is thorough and directly useful for the SPINRISE schema design. QuestPDF 
is used consistently throughout all recommendations — no FastReport 
conflict. The scorecard is honest. TL-Dev Sasi's Stage 0 sign-off, 
Palanivel's TL-IST sign-off dated today, and Saravanan's PM Stage 4 
sign-off dated today are all present.

Mariyaiya, the technical work on this FSD over the past two weeks is 
acknowledged. It reflects sustained effort across multiple rounds of review.


*Two corrections needed — five minutes of work
*
*Correction 1: *Muthuvel's Sr. IST sign-off row is missing from the 
Document Identity table.

The previous version submitted on 13 April had the row: 'SIGNED OFF. 
Sr.IST: MuthuVel — reviewed and approved IST part. Sign-off confirmed 
via email reply. Date: 13-Apr-2026.' That row has been removed in this 
version. It must be restored. Muthuvel is Stage 2 in the review chain 
and his sign-off must be present in the Document Identity table before 
the document can carry CEO approval. The content of his review is in the 
FSD — his name and date simply need to be back in the identity table.

*Correction 2: *TL-IST sign-off row labels Palanivel's review as 'Stage 
4 TL-IST sign-off.'

TL-IST is Stage 3 of the review chain. Stage 4 is the PM. Change the 
wording to: 'APPROVED. TL-IST: Palanivel — Stage 3 TL-IST sign-off 
received and approved via email on 17-Apr-2026.'


*Resubmit with these two corrections*

Restore Muthuvel's Sr. IST sign-off row and correct the Stage 4 label to 
Stage 3 in the TL-IST row. Resubmit as the final version. Both 
corrections take five minutes. Once I receive the corrected document 
with those two rows in the Document Identity table, I will record CEO 
approval.

Regards,
T. Mani

