            <p>Dear Saravanan,<br>
              <br>
              Thank you for submitting the M01 PR Form FSD v2.2 with the
              checklist. I have reviewed both documents in full. <b>The
                FSD content is excellent and I want to acknowledge that
                before addressing the process issue, which is the reason
                I cannot approve this document.<br>
              </b><br>
              <b>What the FSD has achieved</b><br>
              <br>
              <b>Mariyaiya has delivered a thorough FSD.</b> All 20 IST
              questions are resolved. All 12 CEO-directed defects from
              the IST-3, IST-4, and PM feedback are in Section 12 as Rec
              17 through Rec 28. Each has a specific SPINRISE fix.
              Section 5.5a documents the three-level approval workflow
              with Palanivel's confirmation, both web screen names, and
              the URL. Section 10 has the complete web approval screen
              detail. Section 11 includes the Pallavaa division-wise
              stock variation. The ManIndNo duplicate is confirmed and
              resolved. <b>This is the most complete FSD in the project
                and I acknowledge Mariyaiya's work.</b><br>
              <br>
              <b>Muthuvel's Sr.IST Stage 2 sign-off dated 13 April 2026
                is properly recorded in the checklist.<br>
                <br>
              </b><br>
              <b>The problem — and it is a process problem, not a
                content problem</b><br>
